metadata.description:
SPOTLIGHT WK 5

Col3trane pulled up this week with a track off his upcoming EP. Champagne Dial is suave, wildly catchy, and is absolutely gonna be the soundtrack for the next time you ride off into the sunset. 

Here's a quote from LNRZ team member Clear Eyes:

"before i’d ever heard of music nfts i’d heard of Col3trane - his song No Bus with Lophiile is one of my favorite songs point blank period. he’s a crazy skilled writer with a knack for only the dopest production and we’re so proud to highlight him in this weeks spotlight”

Join LNRZ HQ here: https://guild.xyz/lnrz-hq

Visit our website: https://lnrz.xyz/
